description: Pink-hued rocks and small boulders are scattered among the tall grasses lining the headland.  To the west the greyish expanse of Maelstrom Bay sparkles in the moonlight, opening out to the great western sea.  The wind, scented with wild red sorrel, whirls among the grasses, making them shift and bow.
